List MCPServer resources with their Deployment/pod status, image, and pull secrets.

Usage:
  mcp-runtime server status [flags]

Flags:
  -h, --help               help for status
      --namespace string   Namespace to inspect (default "mcp-servers")

Global Flags:
      --debug      Enable debug mode with structured error logging
      --use-kube   Use kubectl and local kubeconfig instead of the platform API for supported commands
